direction: right

User: Client {
  shape: person
}

Cloud: AWS {
  APIGW: API Gateway {
    label: "/orders (POST)"
    style: { stroke: "#FF4F8B" }
  }

  Lambda: Lambda Function {
    label: "Order Processor\n(Python)"
    style: { stroke: "#FF9900"; stroke-width: 2 }
  }

  DynamoDB: DynamoDB Table {
    shape: cylinder
    style: { stroke: "#3F7E44" }
  }
}

User -> Cloud.APIGW: POST JSON
Cloud.APIGW -> Cloud.Lambda: Triggers (Proxy)
Cloud.Lambda -> Cloud.DynamoDB: putItem (IAM Role)

User -> Cloud.Lambda: logs via CloudWatch
